<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Tech Insights Blog</title>

<!-- GOOGLE FONT -->

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
background:#f4f7ff;
color:#222;
line-height:1.7;
}

/* HEADER */

header{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4a6cf7,#6c63ff);
color:white;
padding:40px 8%;
text-align:center;
}

header h1{
font-size:42px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

header p{
font-size:18px;
opacity:0.9;
}

/* BLOG SECTION */

.blog-container{
max-width:1100px;
margin:50px auto;
padding:0 20px;
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
gap:30px;
}

/* BLOG CARD */

.blog-card{
background:white;
border-radius:16px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
transition:0.3s;
}

.blog-card:hover{
transform:translateY(-10px);
box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

/* IMAGE */

.blog-image img{
width:100%;
height:220px;
object-fit:cover;
}

/* CONTENT */

.blog-content{
padding:25px;
}

.blog-content h2{
font-size:24px;
margin-bottom:12px;
color:#4a6cf7;
}

.blog-info{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
flex-wrap:wrap;
font-size:14px;
color:#666;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.blog-content p{
font-size:15px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

/* BUTTON */

.read-btn{
display:inline-block;
padding:10px 20px;
background:#4a6cf7;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:8px;
font-weight:500;
transition:0.3s;
}

.read-btn:hover{
background:#3557e0;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{
background:#111827;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:25px;
margin-top:40px;
}

/* RESPONSIVE */

@media(max-width:768px){

header h1{
font-size:32px;
}

.blog-content h2{
font-size:22px;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HEADER -->

<header>

<h1>Tech Insights Blog</h1>

<p>
Explore the latest trends in Web Development, Artificial Intelligence, and Technology.
</p>

</header>

<!-- BLOG POSTS -->

<section class="blog-container">

<!-- POST 1 -->

<div class="blog-card">

<div class="blog-image">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085" alt="Web Development">

</div>

<div class="blog-content">

<h2>The Future of Web Development</h2>

<div class="blog-info">

<span><i class='bx bx-user'></i> Brundha</span>

<span><i class='bx bx-calendar'></i> May 2026</span>

</div>

<p>
Web development is evolving rapidly with modern frameworks, responsive UI design,
and AI integration transforming user experiences across digital platforms.
</p>

<a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>

</div>

</div>

<!-- POST 2 -->

<div class="blog-card">

<div class="blog-image">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995" alt="AI">

</div>

<div class="blog-content">

<h2>How Artificial Intelligence Improves Productivity</h2>

<div class="blog-info">

<span><i class='bx bx-user'></i> Brundha</span>

<span><i class='bx bx-calendar'></i> April 2026</span>

</div>

<p>
Artificial Intelligence helps automate repetitive tasks, improve workflow efficiency,
and support smart decision-making in modern businesses and startups.
</p>

<a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>

</div>

</div>

<!-- POST 3 -->

<div class="blog-card">

<div class="blog-image">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3" alt="Cyber Security">

</div>

<div class="blog-content">

<h2>Importance of Cyber Security in Modern Technology</h2>

<div class="blog-info">

<span><i class='bx bx-user'></i> Brundha</span>

<span><i class='bx bx-calendar'></i> March 2026</span>

</div>

<p>
Cyber security plays a crucial role in protecting user data, cloud applications,
and digital infrastructure from modern online threats and attacks.
</p>

<a href="#" class="read-btn">Read More</a>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

<footer>

<p>
© 2026 Tech Insights Blog | Designed by Brundha
</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>